<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l14"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . Nu hat vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Bran = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l15"><expan>demb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / ſein <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> dar getan / daʒ man denſelben knecht gemeͣrt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l16">hat . vnd ıſt auch Vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein rechttag <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> Jn geſecʒt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l17">worden auf nu ertag / Alſo ıſt nu der klack ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l18">hat vns geſagt / wıe er ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıte<ex>n</ex></expan> des Panns <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> das plut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l19">ʒu <expan>rıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> niht hab . <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> oder <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu winſpach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l20">hab den Pann . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l21">Jr eẅr <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darcʒu tuet vnd <expan>demſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>amptma<ex>n</ex></expan> gen winſpach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l22"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbet</expan> vnd beſtellet / daʒ er auf dıe <expan>vorge<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> ʒeıt ʒu Rot ſey </ab>
