<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l24"><expan>vb<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> . <expan>ſchedlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> knecht recht gee vnd gerıcht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_463_r1l25">als etc / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
